==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pokerish
<hw>Pok"er*ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Infested by pokers; adapted to
excite fear; <as>as, a <ex>pokerish</ex> place</as>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq. U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There is something <qex>pokerish</qex> about a deserted
dwelling.</q> <rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pokerish</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Pokerish
<hw>Pok"er*ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Stiff like a poker.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Poket</ent>⟦br⟧
